    <h1>CSS Selectors</h1>
    <h2> Applying CSS to Different Parts of HTML</h2>
    
        <p> 1. The elment selector targets elements based on their HTML tag name. </p>
        <p class="classSEL"> 2. Class selectors target elements based on the value of the class attribute.</p>
        <p class="sel2" id="IDSEL"> 3. ID selectors target elements based on the value of the id attribute.</p>
        <p class="attr"> 4. Attribute selectors target elements based on their attributes and values.</p>
        <p class="sel">5. The universal seletor targets all elements.</p>
    
